  pages                      = {615-650},
  volume                     = {64},
  abstract                   = {{We estimate the elasticity of charitable giving with respect to
   persistent and transitory price and income changes using a 1979-2006
   panel of tax returns. Our estimation procedure allows for anticipation
   of and gradual adjustment to tax changes, controls for various potential
